  ** Scanning files: If you have a scanner, you can scan files yourself. Otherwise, scanning services are provided by most printing shops and Internet cafes. Please check that scanned files are readable. <br />
  You can find tips on how to scan documents here: <a href="http://docs.icanlocalize.com/?page_id=151">http://docs.icanlocalize.com/?page_id=151</a>
</p>


